<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Facture {{ facture.numero }}</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 12px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #333;
            background: #fff;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px;
        }
        
        /* Header */
        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #2563eb;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2563eb;
        }
        
        .logo span {
            color: #1e40af;
        }
        
        .facture-info {
            text-align: right;
        }
        
        .facture-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1e40af;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .facture-numero {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        .facture-date {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        
        /* Parties */
        .parties {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        .partie {
            width: 45%;
        }
        
        .partie-title {
            font-size: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .partie-name {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1e40af;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .partie-details {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #555;
        }
        
        .partie-details p {
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }
        
        /* Course Details */
        .course-section {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .section-title {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1e40af;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .course-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .course-item {
            font-size: 11px;
        }
        
        .course-item label {
            display: block;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 3px;
        }
        
        .course-item span {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        /* Table */
        .table-container {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        
        th {
            background: #1e40af;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        th:last-child {
            text-align: right;
        }
        
        td {
            padding: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        td:last-child {
            text-align: right;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .description-cell {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 11px;
        }
        
        /* Totals */
        .totals {
            width: 300px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        .total-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 8px 0;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        .total-row.subtotal {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .total-row.grand-total {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1e40af;
            border-top: 2px solid #1e40af;
            padding-top: 15px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        
        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #666;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        /* Status Badge */
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        .status-issued {
            background: #fef3c7;
            color: #d97706;
        }
        
        .status-paid {
            background: #d1fae5;
            color: #059669;
        }
        
        .status-cancelled {
            background: #fee2e2;
            color: #dc2626;
        }
        
        /* Mentions légales */
        .legal {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #f1f5f9;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 9px;
            color: #64748b;
        }
        
        .legal-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">
                Way<span>Zo</span>
                <div style="font-size: 10px; color: #666; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 5px;">
                    Plateforme VTC
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="facture-info">
                <div class="facture-title">FACTURE</div>
                <div class="facture-numero">N° {{ facture.numero }}</div>
                <div class="facture-date">
                    <p>Date d'émission : {{ facture.dateEmission|date('d/m/Y') }}</p>
                    {% if facture.dateEcheance %}
                    <p>Date d'échéance : {{ facture.dateEcheance|date('d/m/Y') }}</p>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
                <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
                    <span class="status-badge status-{{ facture.statut }}">
                        {% if facture.statut == 'issued' %}En attente{% endif %}
                        {% if facture.statut == 'paid' %}Payée{% endif %}
                        {% if facture.statut == 'cancelled' %}Annulée{% endif %}
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Parties -->
        <div class="parties">
            <div class="partie">
                <div class="partie-title">Émetteur</div>
                <div class="partie-name">{{ facture.emetteurInfo.raisonSociale ?? facture.emetteurInfo.nomComplet }}</div>
                <div class="partie-details">
                    <p>{{ facture.emetteurInfo.nomComplet }}</p>
                    {% if facture.emetteurInfo.adresse %}
                    <p>{{ facture.emetteurInfo.adresse }}</p>
                    {% endif %}
                    <p>{{ facture.emetteurInfo.email }}</p>
                    {% if facture.emetteurInfo.telephone %}
                    <p>Tél : {{ facture.emetteurInfo.telephone }}</p>
                    {% endif %}
                    {% if facture.emetteurInfo.siret %}
                    <p>SIRET : {{ facture.emetteurInfo.siret }}</p>
                    {% endif %}
                    {% if facture.emetteurInfo.tvaIntracom %}
                    <p>TVA Intracom : {{ facture.emetteurInfo.tvaIntracom }}</p>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="partie">
                <div class="partie-title">Destinataire</div>
                <div class="partie-name">{{ facture.destinataireInfo.raisonSociale ?? facture.destinataireInfo.nomComplet }}</div>
                <div class="partie-details">
                    <p>{{ facture.destinataireInfo.nomComplet }}</p>
                    {% if facture.destinataireInfo.adresse %}
                    <p>{{ facture.destinataireInfo.adresse }}</p>
                    {% endif %}
                    <p>{{ facture.destinataireInfo.email }}</p>
                    {% if facture.destinataireInfo.telephone %}
                    <p>Tél : {{ facture.destinataireInfo.telephone }}</p>
                    {% endif %}
                    {% if facture.destinataireInfo.siret %}
                    <p>SIRET : {{ facture.destinataireInfo.siret }}</p>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Course Details -->
        <div class="course-section">
            <div class="section-title">Détails de la course</div>
            <div class="course-grid">
                <div class="course-item">
                    <label>Date & Heure</label>
                    <span>{{ facture.courseDetails.date }} à {{ facture.courseDetails.heure }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="course-item">
                    <label>Client</label>
                    <span>{{ facture.courseDetails.nomClient }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="course-item">
                    <label>Départ</label>
                    <span>{{ facture.courseDetails.depart }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="course-item">
                    <label>Arrivée</label>
                    <span>{{ facture.courseDetails.arrivee }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="course-item">
                    <label>Véhicule</label>
                    <span>{{ facture.courseDetails.vehicule }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="course-item">
                    <label>Passagers</label>
                    <span>{{ facture.courseDetails.passagers }}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Table des prestations -->
        <div class="table-container">
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Désignation</th>
                        <th>Montant</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <strong>Prestation de transport VTC</strong>
                            <div class="description-cell">
                                {{ facture.description|nl2br }}
                            </div>
                        </td>
                        <td>{{ facture.montantHT|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>

        <!-- Totals -->
        <div class="totals">
            <div class="total-row subtotal">
                <span>Total HT</span>
                <span>{{ facture.montantHT|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €</span>
            </div>
            <div class="total-row">
                <span>TVA ({{ facture.tauxTVA }}%)</span>
                <span>{{ facture.montantTVA|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €</span>
            </div>
            <div class="total-row grand-total">
                <span>Total TTC</span>
                <span>{{ facture.montantTTC|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Mentions légales -->
        <div class="legal">
            <div class="legal-title">Mentions légales</div>
            <p>En cas de retard de paiement, une pénalité de 3 fois le taux d'intérêt légal sera appliquée, ainsi qu'une indemnité forfaitaire de 40€ pour frais de recouvrement.</p>
            <p>Pas d'escompte pour paiement anticipé.</p>
            {% if facture.emetteurInfo.siret %}
            <p>SIRET : {{ facture.emetteurInfo.siret }} - {{ facture.emetteurInfo.raisonSociale ?? facture.emetteurInfo.nomComplet }}</p>
            {% endif %}
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Facture générée automatiquement par WayZo - Plateforme de mise en relation VTC</p>
            <p>{{ facture.numero }} | {{ facture.dateEmission|date('d/m/Y H:i') }}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
